Second Department,

February, 1960

(February 23, 1960) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Leonard Wolochen, Appellant.

Motion to dismiss appeal from an order denying, without a hearing, an application in the nature of coram nobis granted and appeal dismissed. (See People v. Wolocken, Motion No. 64, decided herewith.) Present — Nolan, P. J., Ughetta, Kleinfeld, Pette and Brennan, JJ.
